Ext.data.JsonP['Displaying_Dot_Files_and_Folders']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Displaying Dot Files and Folders</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083261\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Displaying Dot Files and Folders</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083261_DisplayingDotFilesandFolders-Overview\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Overview</span></h2>\n    <p>The dot files and folders are hidden by default in App Explorer and Project Explorer views. This page explains how to show them in those views.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083261_DisplayingDotFilesandFolders-Instructions\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Instructions</span></h2>\n    <p>In <strong class=\" \">App Explorer</strong> or <strong class=\" \">Project Explorer</strong> view, click on the drop-down arrow in the view&apos;s local toolbar and select <strong class=\" \">Customize View...</strong>    </p>\n    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083261/customize_view_menu.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083261/customize_view_menu.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n    <br>In the Available Customizations dialog, uncheck the <strong class=\" \">.* resources</strong> entry.    </br></img></p>\n    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083261/customize_view_dialog.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083261/customize_view_dialog.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n    <p>Click <strong class=\" \">OK</strong>. The dot files and folders will now appear.    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083261\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Displaying Dot Files and Folders"});